  <slides>
    <slide type="title">
      <title> How to create a presentation using XSL Transformations </title>
    </slide>

    <slide type="itemize">
      <title> What you will need </title>
      <itemize>
	<item><bold>Saxon</bold>, a xslt processor</item>
	<item>FOP, a xml:fo processor</item>
